{
  "texts": [
    "This initial transformation maps the latent space to a format conducive to 3D volume generation.",
    "This layer is followed by batch normalization and a LeakyReLU activation to introduce non-linearity and stabilize the training process.Conv3DTranspose layers are used to up-sample the volume to the desired dimensions.",
    "G1 is trained only on a dataset of benign pulmonary nodules.",
    "This dataset covers a wide range of benign nodule images.",
    "This is done so that G1 learns to generate varied representations covering both benign nodules' standard and rare features."
  ]
}